                        <interp inst="t18380618-name-196" type="surname" value="FEARNLEY"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18380618-name-196" type="given" value="JOHN"></interp>JOHN FEARNLEY</persName>
                  </hi>. T live in Lincoln's-inn-fields. About half-past four o'clock in the afternoon of the 18th of May, I was walking with a lady in the archway in Lincoln's-inn-fields—I received information, felt in my pocket, and missed my handkerchief—it was afterwards brought to me—this is it—(<hi rend="italic">looking at it</hi>.)</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
                     <persName id="t18380618-name-197" type="witnessName">
